ass-through entity (PTE) election, are not a registered agent, and do not represent clients before any tax authority. Specific city and county TPT rates are framed qualitatively &mdash; confirm any figure against the <a href="https://azdor.gov/business/transaction-privilege-tax/tax-rate-table" rel="noopener nofollow">Arizona Department of Revenue TPT rate table</a>, the <a href="https://azdor.gov/transaction-privilege-tax/contracting-guidelines" rel="noopener nofollow">contracting guidelines</a>, and your CPA.</p>
